const MovieData = [
  {
    id: Math.random(),
    Title: "MAN OF STEEL",
    posterUrl:
      "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/812LjT-we7L._SL1024_.jpg",
    description: `An alien child is 
          evacuated from his dying world 
          and sent to Earth to live among 
          humans. His peace is threatened, 
          when other survivors of his home 
          planet invade Earth.`,
    rate: "2",
  },
  {
    id: Math.random(),
    Title: "MINORITY REPORT",
    posterUrl:
      "https://i.pinimg.com/564x/51/3b/67/513b67ed8444c776fa860beaf1e35e82.jpg",
    description: `Based on a story by famed science fiction writer Philip K. Dick, "Minority Report" is an 
    action-detective thriller set in Washington D.C. in 2054, where police utilize a psychic technology to 
    arrest and convict murderers before they commit their crime.`,
    rate: "2",
  },
  {
    id: Math.random(),
    Title: "GAME OF THRONES ",
    posterUrl:
      "https://i.pinimg.com/564x/53/8c/56/538c56de7726c6109640f410e55b2a30.jpg",
    description: `Game of Thrones is an HBO series that tells the story of a medieval country's civil war.`,
    rate: "5",
  },
];
export default MovieData;
